token_lists.title: Xerox/Copy/Retro Vibes
token_lists.description: Pieces with that certain element of imperfect print, cognizant of a copy machines past. In a society where perfection is treasured and almost standardized, heres a 'retro' blast from the past of pieces which celebrate imperfection or emulate a printers past.

token_lists.title: Futurism
token_lists.description: The 1960's Worlds Fair inspired thousands of individuals to conceptualize the future they want to live in. Attendee's could explore this future at the fair, immersing themselves in a seemingly not so distant reality. At some point over the past few decades we have lost that imaginative vision. This board is my attempt to find contemporary examples of NFTs which reflect both a utopian or dystopian reality. Hope you enjoy, but really hope these images inspire you to conceptualize the future as well. :)

token_lists.title: Avatars & Meta-Humans
token_lists.description: What is the Avatars and Meta-Humans Board about?: A 3D scan of ourselves. A digital humanoid controlled by invisible forces (creator) in an interactive virtual world. This beings lives in different metaverses in Virtual, Augmented or Mixed Reality. These metaverses may be inspired by real places but they are mostly based on unreal spaces where we have always dreamed of being.
